## 🔑 9. KEY OPTIMIZATIONS SUMMARY

| Strategi | Penghematan | Cara Kerja |
|---|---|---|
| **🧠 3-Tier Memory** | ~70% token | Hanya kirim yang relevan, bukan semua history |
| **🔀 Model Routing** | ~60% cost | Query simple → model murah, complex → model pintar |
| **📦 Compression** | ~80% storage | Summarize old conversations jadi compact |
| **⚡ Response Cache** | 100% (cache hit) | Pertanyaan identik → instant response |
| **🔍 Semantic Search** | ~90% token | Top-3 relevant memory vs entire history |
| **📉 Memory Decay** | Storage savings | Auto-archive memory yang tidak pernah diakses |
| **🏃 Async Post-process** | Faster UX | Extract facts & compress SETELAH response dikirim |
| **📏 Rule-based Classifier** | 0 extra token | Classify query tanpa API call |

